snippet.title: Relic Hunters Zero Beta - Dev Let's Play (60fps)
snippet.description:
I apologize for the audio quality, there are closed captions available and I recommend them.

Jimmy gameplay starts on 0:42
Pinkyy gameplay starts on 7:20
